  "management45": "Critical operational constraints are flagged at 16 airports right now. No engine anti-ice operations are currently flagged. Across base airports: 7 critical, 12 high, 12 medium, 8 normal. Key bases needing attention include London Gatwick (LGW/EGKK), Cluj Avram Iancu (CLJ/LRCL) and Chişinău (RMO/LUKK); plus 16 other bases. 12 additional base airports are at medium severity and should be monitored closely. At base airports, the dominant pattern is snow-related runway contamination risk, mist and cold‑temperature performance penalties  — most notably around Chişinău (RMO/LUKK), Belgrade Nikola Tesla (BEG/LYBE) and Gdańsk Lech Wałęsa (GDN/EPGD). Network hotspots: Kaunas (KUN/EYKA), Turku (TKU/EFTU), Gdańsk Lech Wałęsa (GDN/EPGD), Modlin (WMI/EPMO), Warsaw Chopin (WAW/EPWA) and 11 others. Primary drivers: snow / blowing snow, low cloud base and mist. Expected impact is reduced runway capacity with higher delay and diversion risk, especially where visibility/RVR and cloud base are very low. Since the last update, 12 airports changed status, led by Turku (TKU/EFTU), Almaty (ALA/UAAA), Trondheim Airport, Værnes (TRD/ENVA) and 9 others.",
  "detail90": "Critical operational constraints are flagged at 16 airports right now. Base airports (focus): London Gatwick (LGW/EGKK) — HIGH: mist; strong gusts risk; cloud base around 200 ft | Cluj Avram Iancu (CLJ/LRCL) — HIGH: mist; snow; visibility down to 1.5 km, cloud base around 500 ft | Chişinău (RMO/LUKK) — CRIT: snow; cold-temperature performance penalties; visibility down to 500 m, cloud base around 400 ft | Sibiu (SBZ/LRSB) — HIGH: mist; snow; cold-temperature performance penalties | Timişoara Traian Vuia (TSR/LRTR) — HIGH: fog; visibility down to 600 m, cloud base around 200 ft | Tirana International Airport Mother Teresa (TIA/LATI) — HIGH: thunderstorm / convective risk and 13 others. Worst affected now: Kaunas (KUN/EYKA) — CRIT: mist; snow; runway contamination risk (drivers: approach minima limits, runway contamination / reduced braking, cold-temperature performance penalties) | Turku (TKU/EFTU) — CRIT: snow; cold-temperature performance penalties; strong gusts risk (drivers: runway visual range (RVR) constraints, cold-temperature performance penalties, very low visibility) | Gdańsk Lech Wałęsa (GDN/EPGD) — CRIT: mist; snow; runway contamination risk (drivers: crosswind limitations, runway contamination / reduced braking, cold-temperature performance penalties) | Modlin (WMI/EPMO) — CRIT: fog; snow; cold-temperature performance penalties (drivers: low-visibility takeoff restrictions, runway visual range (RVR) constraints, cold-temperature performance penalties) | Warsaw Chopin (WAW/EPWA) — CRIT: fog; snow; cold-temperature performance penalties (drivers: low-visibility takeoff restrictions, runway visual range (RVR) constraints, cold-temperature performance penalties) | Göteborg Landvetter (GOT/ESGG) — CRIT: fog; snow; cold-temperature performance penalties (drivers: low-visibility procedures (reduced capacity), runway visual range (RVR) constraints, cold-temperature performance penalties) and 10 others. Changed since last run: Turku (TKU/EFTU), Almaty (ALA/UAAA), Trondheim Airport, Værnes (TRD/ENVA), Tirana International Airport Mother Teresa (TIA/LATI), Skopje (SKP/LWSK), Oslo-Gardermoen (OSL/ENGM), Sandefjord Airport, Torp (TRF/ENTO), Nuremberg (NUE/EDDN), Stavanger Airport, Sola (SVG/ENZV), Ohrid St. Paul the Apostle (OHD/LWOH) and 2 others.",
